  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-04 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation evidence was generated under solver configuration ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which the assessment team characterised as effectively identical to the released build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7; no re-run of validation cases was performed under the released version. Decision: Accepted.",
